OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,FA coroner has said there is "no causal
OL,7,Flink" between the appearance of a
OL,8,Fguest on The Jeremy Kyle Show and his
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FSteve Dymond, 63, from Portsmouth,
OL,12,FHampshire, took his own life seven
OL,13,Fdays after filming for the ITV show in
OL,14,FMay 2019.
OL,16,FCoroner Jason Pegg recorded a verdict
OL,17,Fof death by suicide.
