OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,FMr Pegg said, "I have been invited to
OL,7,Fconsider the evidence as to whether
OL,8,Fthe comments and treatment by Jeremy
OL,9,FKyle during Steve Dymond's
OL,10,Fparticipation in the recording of the
OL,11,Fshow contributed to his adverse mental
OL,12,Fstate."
OL,14,F"There is insufficient evidence for me
OL,15,Fto be satisfied that this was the
OL,16,Fdirect cause of Steve Dymond's
OL,17,Fdistress. There is evidence available
OL,18,Fto me at this particular time of other
OL,19,Fstressors to Steve Dymond's life."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
