OL,6,F"I have been invited to consider
OL,7,Fevidence in support of this assertion
OL,8,Fwhich includes hearsay comments to
OL,9,Ffamily members, and friends.
OL,11,F"These accounts are not supported with
OL,12,Fany independent expert evidence to
OL,13,Fevaluate the impact of his treatment
OL,14,Fon the show.
