OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"Having considered the evidence
OL,7,Fcarefully there is an absence of
OL,8,Freliable evidence that demonstrates
OL,9,Fthat Steve Dymond's appearance on the
OL,10,FJeremy Kyle Show probably caused or
OL,11,Fcontributed to his death to do so
OL,12,Fwould be speculative.
OL,14,F"I am not satisfied that events on
OL,15,FJeremy Kyle Show gave rise to a clear
OL,16,Flink that caused or contributed to the
OL,17,Fdeath of Steve Dymond such that I
OL,18,Fshould be recording this as a
OL,19,Fcontributing factor.
