OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"Steve Dymond had a history of a
OL,7,Fdiagnosed personality disorder and
OL,8,Fmental illness which presented on a
OL,9,Fnumber of occasions before any
OL,10,Fappearance of the show and resulted in
OL,11,Fself-harming or displaying thoughts of
OL,12,Fsuicide."
OL,14,FJeremy Kyle has described how the
OL,15,F"false accusations" against him since
OL,16,FSteve Dymond's death had taken a "huge
OL,17,Ftoll on him and his family".
