OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,FIn a statement released after the
OL,7,Finquest, he said, "His Majesty's
OL,8,FCoroner has today clearly and
OL,9,Funequivocally found that Jeremy Kyle
OL,10,Fdid not in any way cause or contribute
OL,11,Fto the tragic suicide of Steve Dymond.
OL,13,F"He is now exonerated of that ill-
OL,14,Finformed accusation and his name has
OL,15,Ffinally been cleared.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
