OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"Out of respect for the family of Mr
OL,7,FDymond and the judicial process,
OL,8,FJeremy has always maintained that it
OL,9,Fwould be inappropriate to discuss
OL,10,Fdetails whilst the legal inquest was
OL,11,Fongoing and he has remained
OL,12,Fsteadfastly silent in the face of
OL,13,Flies, false accusations and unfair
OL,14,Fcriticism over the last 5 1/2 years.
OL,16,F"This has taken a huge toll on him and
OL,17,Fhis family and he would like to thank
OL,18,Feveryone who has truly supported him
OL,19,Fthrough these tough times."
