OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,FA family statement was read outside
OL,7,Fthe Coroner's court by lawyer, Anna
OL,8,FThwaites, on behalf of Steve Dymond's
OL,9,Fson, Carl Woolley.
OL,11,F"It has been five years since my
OL,12,Ffather died. In my view, anyone
OL,13,Fwatching the clips of the show can see
OL,14,Fthat he was in tears and spoken to in
OL,15,Fthe most brutal way by Jeremy Kyle."
OL,17,F"The Coroner has recorded that the lie
OL,18,Fdetector test, in which Jeremy Kyle
OL,19,Fbelieves so strongly, can have an
OL,20,Faccuracy of 60 to 96 per cent."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
