OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"The only good thing that came of my
OL,7,Ffather's death is The Jeremy Kyle Show
OL,8,Fis cancelled."
OL,10,FIn response to the inquest, ITV
OL,11,Freleased a statement saying, "We
OL,12,Fextend our deepest sympathies to those
OL,13,Fclose to Mr Dymond and recognise how
OL,14,Fdifficult the inquest and the past
OL,15,Ffive years have been for them."
OL,17,F"The Coroner did not find any causal
OL,18,Flink between Steve Dymond's appearance
OL,19,Fon The Jeremy Kyle Show and his death."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
