OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"In the Coroner's findings of fact he
OL,7,Fconfirmed that The Jeremy Kyle Show
OL,8,Fhad comprehensive Duty of Care
OL,9,Fprocesses covering the selection of
OL,10,Fcontributors who appeared on the show
OL,11,Fand their care both during and after
OL,12,Ffilming."
OL,14,F"The Coroner described how these
OL,15,Fprocesses were followed with Steve
OL,16,FDymond including the offer of follow
OL,17,Fup Cognitive Behavioural Therapy
OL,18,Fsupport."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
