OL,3,CCoroner says The Jeremy Kyle Show not
OL,4,Cto blame for Steve Dymond death
OL,6,F"ITV is committed to continuing to
OL,7,Fevolve and strengthen the care given
OL,8,Fto all those who take part in our
OL,9,Fshows which we believe set industry
OL,10,Fleading standards for the selection,
OL,11,Fprotection and support of
OL,12,Fparticipants."
OL,14,FMr Dymond had been diagnosed with a
OL,15,Fdepressive disorder in 1995 and had
OL,16,Ftaken overdoses on four occasions ` in
OL,17,FJanuary 1995, twice in December 2002
OL,18,Fand in April 2005, the court was told.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
